Source: paintown
Section: games
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Savvas Radevic <vicedar@gmail.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 7), libsdl-dev, scons (>= 1.1.0), libpng12-dev, 
 libfreetype6-dev, zlib1g-dev, libmad0-dev, python-dev, libvorbis-dev,
 libogg-dev, libmpg123-dev
Homepage: http://paintown.sf.net
Standards-Version: 3.9.2

Package: paintown
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, paintown-data (=${source:Version})
Description: Paintown is a 2-d fighting game similar to Streets of Rage
 and Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. Paintown comes with level and animation 
 editors to help with the creation of new content. Paintown also implements the
 MUGEN engine.
 .
 This package contains the arch dependent binary files.

Package: paintown-data
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: paintown
Description: A 2-d fighting game similar to Streets of Rage
 and Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles. Paintown comes with level and animation 
 editors to help with the creation of new content. Paintown also implements the
 MUGEN engine. You can download the data files from 
 https://paintown.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/paintown/data
 .
 This package contains the arch independent data files.

